Class SqlCreate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.sql.SqlNode

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SqlCreateForeignSchema, SqlCreateFunction, SqlCreateMaterializedView, SqlCreateSchema, SqlCreateTable, SqlCreateType, SqlCreateView

    public abstract class SqlCreate
extends SqlDdl
    Base class for an CREATE statements parse tree nodes. The portion of the statement covered by this class is "CREATE [ OR REPLACE ]". Subclasses handle whatever comes afterwards.
